01:11:35.430 --> 01:11:36.830
Okay, I will.

01:11:38.510 --> 01:11:39.950
I love you.

01:11:43.350 --> 01:11:45.750
I love you, Jack.

01:11:46.590 --> 01:11:49.510
Tell Sam I love him so much.

01:11:51.030 --> 01:11:52.950
God be with you.

